UPDATED BISD Lunch Pick-Up and Drop-Off Information;

Beginning March 30th BISD food delivery volunteers will be delivering breakfast sacks AND lunch sacks in one delivery each day. Drop off locations will remain the same and at the same time each day.

UPDATED BES PICK UP TIME CHANGE... pick-up is now from 11:00 to 12:30 each day.

